main event: A UFO report from Project Blue Book concerning sightings in Garden City, Michigan on April 19, 1966.
interesting points: The report includes 2 grainy black and white photographs of the unidentified aerial object.,The photos show the object against a cloudy or hazy background.,Branches or twigs are visible in the foreground of the first photo.,The object is described as small and obscured in the images.,The report is unclassified by the Foreign Technology Division, AFSC.
